<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_f303f25fdaee.aspx"><b>椒聊</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonf303f25fdaee">
<p>椒聊之实，蕃衍盈升。彼其之子，硕大无朋。椒聊且，远条且。<br />椒聊之实，蕃衍盈匊。彼其之子，硕大且笃。椒聊且，远条且。</p>
